root: ^I found this key, is it yours?
^No, my key is in my pocket.
^Oh, well maybe this is a duplicate.
^Also impossible. I replaced the lock myself. There's no reason for him to be in there looking through my stuff.
^I see. But are you sure this isn't your key?
^Well, it does look similar. Very similar. That's odd.
^Wait!? This is the same key! But, how?
^This day is full of surprises, isn't it?
^She never lost her key before the murder happened. It only makes sense, the murderer stole her key.
